<h2>Groups I&#8217;ve been with for some time</h2>
<ul><li><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://astro.fisica.unimib.it/" target="_blank">Astrophysics group</a> at Milan-Bicocca</li><li><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.sr.bham.ac.uk/gwgroup/" target="_blank">Institute for Gravitational Wave Astronomy</a> in Birmingham</li><li> <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.tapir.caltech.edu/" target="_blank">TAPIR</a> at Caltech</li><li>Cambridge <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.ctc.cam.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Center for Theoretical Cosmology</a></li><li><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.phy.olemiss.edu/GR" target="_blank">Gravitational physics group</a> at OleMiss</li><li><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://astro.fisica.unimi.it/" target="_blank">Theoretical Astrophysics Group</a> at the University of Milan</li></ul>
